code: @Test public void testTokenize() throws InterruptedException {     template.setDefaultEndpointUri("direct:tokenize").     // warm up with 1 message so that the JIT compiler kicks in     execute(1).     resetMock(count).     StopWatch watch = new StopWatch().     execute(1).     assertMockEndpointsSatisfied().     log.warn("Ran {} tests in {}ms", count, watch.taken()). }

@Override protected RouteBuilder createRouteBuilder() throws Exception {     return new RouteBuilder() {          public void configure() throws Exception {             from("direct:tokenize").split(body().tokenize("\n")).to("mock:end").         }     }. }
